# Important note: one misleading variable name

This config field:

```javascript
attraction: 0xfa0
```

is actually used like this:

```javascript
force = attraction / (dist * dist)
dx = node1.x - node2.x
...
node1.vx += fx
node2.vx -= fx
```

That is **repulsion**, not attraction. So the name is misleading.

